        "text": "The “Art of the Unmatched” is our trademarked design philosophy and it’s the basis, foundation and inspiration for our collection each season. The word unmatched is intentional – different than mismatched, unmatched is purposeful, varied, and unexpected, resembling each of our personal histories and lives. The Art of the Unmatched™ is representative of journey; a collage of sights, sounds, emotions, and travels.",
